-- Campeonato Brasileiro Série A — 19 real clubs.
-- Combined with Brassfoot FC (migration 0002, country='BR') this gives exactly
-- 20 BR teams, matching the real Brasileirão and producing a clean 38-round
-- double round-robin when a league is created with country="BR".
--
-- Composition is based on the approximate 2025 Série A roster. The 4 C-tier
-- entries (Santos, Sport Recife, Ceará, Novorizontino) reflect the likely
-- promoted clubs from Série B 2024; exact composition may vary.
--
-- PLAYER NAMES ARE FICTIONAL — plausible Brazilian-sounding names that are
-- NOT real athletes. Attributes reflect each club's relative competitive tier:
--   S-tier (top 4):   overall ~82–90
--   A-tier (mid 8):   overall ~78–84
--   B-tier (next 4):  overall ~72–78
--   C-tier (bottom 3): overall ~68–73
-- Squad format mirrors the rest of the project: 1 GK / 4 DEF / 4 MID / 3 FWD.

